{"tid":492371,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"28年倉底劇重見天日！黎明擔正《晉文公傳奇》深夜時段出街","createTime":"2017-12-07T12:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T14:45:41.000Z","uid":4420,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ac1771bba4a1bdee799a1f41c5450bdb9cf2de","tid":492371,"uid":4420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"無綫每年拍攝多部劇集，但有部分劇集會因為各種原因，只係喺海外市場或者收費台播出。好似《蘭花劫》就喺倉底擺咗十年，先正式喺翡翠台出街。就算神劇《天與地》都要擺咗兩年先播。唔係每部倉底劇都咁好彩可以重見天日，有啲劇可能永無見天之日。<br />\n<br />\n網上有消息指，TVB將會安排28年前倉底劇《晉文公傳奇》，喺下年1月初深宵時段緊貼《壹號皇庭V》播放。《晉文公傳奇》由黎明、羅慧娟、郭秀雲、及歐陽震華主演，於1989年拍攝，不過一直都冇喺免費電視頻道播放，只係出咗DVD同埋向海外發行。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝《晉文公傳奇 》時黎明只得23歲，劇照中睇到當時嘅黎明非常青澀靚仔，呢套劇亦都喺佢首次擔正做男主角，仲早過另一套成名作《天涯歌女》。劇中黎明飾演晉文公重耳，講述晉文公點樣喺重重難關下，成為晉國國君。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EnWCb0DoF1KsdsufXXSTsQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgxO2g9NDc5O2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/1beec60cb8f5c143af47589eb826fe98/tumblr_inline_p0kw8l7CJF1u03abq_1280.png.cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEnWCb0DoF1KsdsufXXSTsQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgxO2g9NDc5O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F1beec60cb8f5c143af47589eb826fe98%2Ftumblr_inline_p0kw8l7CJF1u03abq_1280.png.cf.jpg&h=96c38daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/s1bQ6UnHurNomToBb_IlWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NDgwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/98dc27e66d1ae166e0b8c64f58aec298/tumblr_inline_p0kw8udTLV1u03abq_1280.png.cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fs1bQ6UnHurNomToBb_IlWw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NDgwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F98dc27e66d1ae166e0b8c64f58aec298%2Ftumblr_inline_p0kw8udTLV1u03abq_1280.png.cf.jpg&h=c9e0e335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pC0yP6Hvu8yhjsOHmFKhrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt